{"tid":971301,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 操 肌 盼 影 寫 真","createTime":"2019-01-06T13:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T11:39:55.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cd93b35dc02a8621eeaec5acc1bd8a37abfbbecf","tid":971301,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:53:04.000Z","msg":"吳業坤昨日與谷婭溦到土瓜灣出席活動時，谷婭溦因撞車遲到，她說：「入隧道嗰陣俾人追尾，人冇事但好驚，上年都俾人撞過，我會去拜神。」<br />\n<br />\n坤哥於台上獻唱時飛釘，事後他笑指是人之常情，又謂想操六嚿腹肌：「到時慳番啲服裝錢，仲要影寫真。」問到可會接受露股演出？他說：「我對前面有信心啲，都係睇劇情需要啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190106/large/06ec2p4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190106%2Flarge%2F06ec2p4a.jpg&h=1f1a79eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8f3a274de3a260e349ee8de8faad255119444c8","tid":971301,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:58:11.000Z","msg":"剃光埋佢"},{"pid":"3a440ca882b678e487cb7d2c63662f86c217fa69","tid":971301,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b940e672fae68826e11e1a5a44fcd31c5f457f5f","tid":971301,"uid":10451,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T17:35:06.000Z","msg":"發夢嘅時候識佢個健身導師，話坤哥懶到出汁，根本唔會操到出嚟"},{"pid":"d8f9b5d22829b97001d6357b4dec922d1fc94a41","tid":971301,"uid":121130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:50:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾 唔好理佢會自動消失"},{"pid":"4d77e13d3b85382349d9564cef550d277ad3b1f1","tid":971301,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:39:55.000Z","msg":"佢條眉咁嘅 係咪拜得多狐仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}